@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@json = application/json
@taskId = task-tracking-switch-staged-001

### Tracking manual switch staged test
### Focus APIs:
### 1) auto-generated /tasks/manual-switch/request record (query by GET)
### 2) POST /tasks/manual-switch/feedback
###
### Boundary with select scenario:
### - select: no explicit designated target, system asks for manual selection.
### - switch: explicit designated target already exists, system asks whether to switch.
###
### Scenario:
### - Stage-1 inject only designated original target and verify stable tracking.
### - Stage-2 inject higher-value targets.
### - system auto-sends manual-switch request (up to 2 higher-value candidates) and starts 20s countdown.
### - query switch send status via GET, then choose feedback branch.

### 1. Reset local mock state
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/reset

### 2. Set ownship initial state OUTSIDE task area
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/navigation
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "platform_id": 1001,
  "speed_mps": 6.2,
  "heading_deg": 90.0,
  "longitude": 120.5000000,
  "latitude": 30.2200000,
  "timestamp": "2026-04-01T12:00:00Z"
}

### 3. Stage-1 inject ONLY original designated target
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/perception
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "target_count": 1,
  "targets": [
    {
      "source_platform_id": 2001,
      "target_id": "target-origin-001",
      "target_batch_no": 2101,
      "target_bearing_deg": 88.0,
      "target_distance_m": 1800,
      "target_absolute_speed_mps": 6.0,
      "target_absolute_heading_deg": 90.0,
      "target_longitude": 121.5120000,
      "target_latitude": 31.2200000,
      "target_type_code": 106,
      "military_civil_attr": 1,
      "target_name": "target-origin-001",
      "threat_level": 2,
      "timestamp": "2026-04-01T12:00:00Z",
      "active": true
    }
  ]
}

### 4. Create tracking task with explicit designated target (switch scenario precondition)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "task_id": "{{taskId}}",
  "task_type": "tracking",
  "task_name": "tracking-switch-staged-test",
  "task_source": "planning_service",
  "priority": 1,
  "mode": "escort",
  "target_info": {
    "target_id": "target-origin-001",
    "target_batch_no": 2101,
    "target_type_code": 106,
    "threat_level": 2,
    "target_name": "target-origin-001",
    "military_civil_attr": 1
  },
  "task_area": {
    "area_type": "polygon",
    "points": [
      { "longitude": 121.49, "latitude": 31.21 },
      { "longitude": 121.55, "latitude": 31.21 },
      { "longitude": 121.55, "latitude": 31.24 },
      { "longitude": 121.49, "latitude": 31.24 }
    ]
  },
  "expected_speed": 12.0,
  "update_interval_sec": 1,
  "end_condition": {
    "duration_sec": 300,
    "out_of_region_finish": true
  },
  "linkage_param": {
    "enable_optical": true,
    "enable_evidence": true
  }
}

### 5. Simulate planning feasibility callback
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/callbacks/planning/feasibility
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "task_id": "{{taskId}}",
  "plan_type": "patrol",
  "feasible": true,
  "reason": "route accepted by planning",
  "suggested_action": "continue",
  "callback_time": "2026-04-01T12:00:05Z"
}

### 6. Move ownship into task area
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/navigation
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "platform_id": 1001,
  "speed_mps": 6.2,
  "heading_deg": 90.0,
  "longitude": 121.5000000,
  "latitude": 31.2200000,
  "timestamp": "2026-04-01T12:00:06Z"
}

### 7. Verify stage-1 tracking target
### Expected: current_target_id = target-origin-001
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/result

