### 9. Inspect result after stage-2 perception
### Expected: still tracking original target until switch feedback
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/result

### 10. Inspect auto-generated manual switch request logs
### If empty, wait 1-2 seconds and query again (decision loop is 1s)
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/collaboration/manual-switch/requests

### 11. Inspect manual switch status (auto-send + 20s timer)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/manual-switch/status

### 12. Choose one branch below (A or B), do not execute both

### ====================
### Branch A: no feedback in 20s -> keep original target
### ====================

### A1. Do not send feedback. Wait at least 20 seconds from request_time in status endpoint.

### A2. Verify task keeps original target
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/result

### A3. Re-check manual switch status (pending should be false)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/manual-switch/status

### ====================
### Branch B: feedback in 20s -> switch to designated target
### ====================

### B1. Send manual switch feedback within 20 seconds
### Note: feedback_time is recorded only; timeout check uses server current time.
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/manual-switch/feedback
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "task_id": "{{taskId}}",
  "selected_target_id": "target-high-001",
  "keep_current": false,
  "feedback_time": "2026-04-01T00:00:00Z"
}

### B2. Inspect manual switch feedback logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/collaboration/manual-switch/feedbacks

### B3. Verify switched target
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/result

### B4. Re-check manual switch status (feedback_received should be true)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/manual-switch/status

### 13. Inspect autonomy tracking logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/autonomy/tracking/logs


### 6. Move ownship into task area
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/navigation
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "platform_id": 1001,
  "speed_mps": 6.2,
  "heading_deg": 90.0,
  "longitude": 121.50374190927708,
  "latitude": 31.22049989305282,
  "timestamp": "2026-04-01T12:00:06Z"
}

### 14. Inspect optical linkage commands
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/collaboration/optical-linkage/commands

### 15. Inspect media stream access logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/collaboration/media/stream-access

### 16. Cleanup task
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/terminate
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "reason": "cleanup"
}


